Platinum Business Magazine - Issue 11, 2015

Platinum Business Magazine was born out of the desire to give Sussex a world class business publication. Sussex is one of the powerhouse regions of the country and deserves a business magazine with a fiercely independent editorial outlook, no poorly disguised advertorials, an informative and entertaining read and an editorial stance that speaks directly to business leaders across the entire South East region, regardless of the size of the company.

Our aim is to ensure the magazine is stylish, contemporary and national in appearance but with regional content.
